PrecisSanction of the trackage rights agreements between the CANADIAN PACIFIC LIMITED (CP) and the ESSEX TERMINAL RAILWAY COMPANY (ETR) concerning the granting to CP of trackage connections between the proposed railway yard of CP in Windsor, Ontario and the old railway yard of CP north of Tecumseh Road West, in Windsor; and the granting of inter-yard transfer movements by ETR accross trackage of CP.
